		<p>Is the butter salted or not?</p>
<p class="thdrpy">[<a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="movecfm(event,25691,1,'Kaitlin');">Reply</a>]</p><div class="comment-childs chalt" id="comment-25830"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/4a11bc1e9b9a0b651dd18e1a8a91f912?s=32&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F0.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D32&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32 photo' height='32' width='32' /><p><cite>Megan</cite> Reply:<br /><small class="commentmetadata">June 8th, 2011 at 8:53 am</small></p><p>@Kaitlin,<br />
